textBox.richText: This weekend was *COLD*...highs in the low single digits. Got 6” of snow friday; tried out the Graphite Zoom. Note to self: not a good wax for uber-cold. Did the CH4 on Sunday....while it’s still not good, it’s *MUCH* better. Max had freestyle comp #1; he’s now in J5s, so significantly more competition (some of those boys were throwing 360s off the jump). He still keeps looking better and better. He’d go and do a practice run or two, come in and warm up, then head back out. Vid below...
